Command> gh issue list    # イシューの一覧表示

Keywords> github
        > issue

Description>
           > $ gh issue list --web              # ブラウザを開いて表示
           > $ gh issue list --search "hoge"    # hogeに関して検索
           > $ gh issue list [-a | --assignee] [login name]
           > $ gh issue list [-A | --author] [string]   # 作成者名で絞り込む
           > $ gh issue list [-l | --label] [label name]
           > $ gh issue list [-L | --limit] [print num]
           > $ gh issue list [--mention] [@name]  # メンション名で絞り込む
           > $ gh issue list [-m | --milestone] [number]   # マイルストーンで絞り込み
           > $ gh issue list [-s | --state] [open | close | all]
           > $ gh issue list [-w | --web]

Scene01> gh issue list --label "bug" --label "help wanted"
Scene02> gh issue list --author monalisa
Scene03> gh issue list --assignee "@me"
Scene04> gh issue list --milestone "The big 1.0"
Scene05> gh issue list --search "error no:assignee sort:created-asc"


Reference> https://dev.classmethod.jp/articles/i-tried-operations-around-issue-with-github-cli-20/
         > https://zenn.dev/gashi/articles/6a9b7bf2b9dfe79e3870
